longBusinessSummary: AJIS Co., Ltd. provides inventory and other retail support services in Asia. The company's retail support services include store inventory, logistics warehouse inventory, inventory inspection, asset inventory, and disaster stockpile management business consignment services, as well as merchandising, research, promotion, staffing, and consulting services. Its products are used for retail, manufacturers, store owners, warehouses, and public consumers. The company was incorporated in 1978 and is headquartered in Chiba, Japan.
